-- Update Donchian Channel / High-Low Strategy
UPDATE learning_articles SET content = content || E'\n\n## Practice Trade Setup: Crude Oil Donchian Channel Example\n\n**Scenario:** CL (Crude Oil) 20-day high breakout\n\n**Setup Details:**\n- **Instrument:** WTI Crude Oil (CL)\n- **Timeframe:** Daily\n- **Channel Period:** 20 days\n- **20-Day High:** $78.50\n- **20-Day Low:** $72.00\n\n**Trade Execution (Turtle Rules):**\n1. **Long Entry:** $78.75 (break above 20-day high)\n2. **Stop Loss (10-day low):** $75.20 (exit on 10-day low break, $3.55 risk)\n3. **Trailing Stop:** 2x ATR(20) = 2 × $1.50 = $3.00\n4. **Add Position:** Every 0.5 ATR of profit ($0.75)\n\n**Position Sizing (Turtle Method):**\n- Account: $100,000\n- ATR(20): $1.50\n- 1 ATR Risk: $1,500 per contract (1,000 barrels)\n- Risk 1% = $1,000\n- Position: $1,000 / $1,500 = 0.67 contracts → 1 contract\n\n**Unit Adding:**\n- Unit 1: $78.75 entry\n- Unit 2: $79.50 (add at +0.5 ATR with profit)\n- Unit 3: $80.25 (add at +1.0 ATR with profit)\n- Maximum: 4 units per market\n\n**Exit Rules:**\n- Exit all on 10-day low break ($75.20 initially, trailing)\n- Or exit on 2N trailing stop'
WHERE slug = 'high-low-channel-strategy';

-- Update Swing Trading Strategy
