-- Update Head and Shoulders Trading
UPDATE learning_articles SET content = content || E'\n\n## Practice Trade Setup: Head and Shoulders Short\n\n**Scenario:** EUR/GBP forms head and shoulders at resistance\n\n**Setup Details:**\n- **Pair:** EUR/GBP\n- **Timeframe:** 4-Hour\n- **Pattern Duration:** 3 weeks\n\n**Pattern Points:**\n- Left Shoulder High: 0.8650\n- Head High: 0.8720\n- Right Shoulder High: 0.8640\n- Neckline: 0.8550 (connecting lows)\n\n**Trade Execution:**\n1. **Entry:** 0.8535 (neckline break with confirmation candle)\n2. **Stop Loss:** 0.8660 (above right shoulder, 125 pips)\n3. **Target:** 0.8365 (pattern height projection: 0.8720-0.8550=170 pips)\n4. **Risk:Reward:** 1:1.36\n\n**Position Sizing:**\n- Account: $15,000\n- Risk: 1.5% = $225\n- Stop: 125 pips\n- Position: 0.18 lots\n\n**Pattern Validation:**\n- Left and right shoulders roughly equal height ✓\n- Head clearly higher than both shoulders ✓\n- Neckline slope: Slightly rising (stronger signal)\n- Volume: Declining from left shoulder to head to right shoulder ✓\n- RSI divergence at head (lower high in RSI) ✓'
WHERE slug = 'head-shoulders-trading';

-- Update Volume Spread Analysis
UPDATE learning_articles SET content = content || E'\n\n## Practice Trade Setup: VSA Climactic Action\n\n**Scenario:** Selling climax followed by test\n\n**Setup Details:**\n- **Stock:** Meta (META)\n- **Timeframe:** Daily\n- **Context:** Downtrend approaching major support\n\n**VSA Sequence:**\n1. **Climactic Bar:** Large down bar, ultra-high volume, closes off lows\n   - Range: $15 (high $290, low $275, close $282)\n   - Volume: 5x average (distribution complete)\n   \n2. **Automatic Rally:** 3 green bars on decreasing volume\n   - Price: $282 → $295\n   \n3. **Test Bar:** Down bar, LOW volume, tests $278\n   - Range: $8, Volume: 0.5x average\n   - Closes in middle of range\n\n**Trade Execution:**\n1. **Entry:** $285.00 (next candle after successful low-volume test)\n2. **Stop Loss:** $272.00 (below climax low, $13 risk)\n3. **Target 1:** $305.00 (1.5:1 R:R)\n4. **Target 2:** $320.00 (prior swing high, 2.7:1 R:R)\n\n**Position Sizing:**\n- Account: $40,000\n- Risk: 2% = $800\n- Stop: $13\n- Position: $800 / $13 = 61 shares\n\n**VSA Confirmation:**\n- Climax bar: Wide spread, high volume, close off lows ✓\n- Test bar: Narrow spread, low volume, holds above climax low ✓\n- No supply: Test proves sellers exhausted ✓'
WHERE slug = 'volume-spread-analysis';

-- Update Flags and Pennants Trading
UPDATE learning_articles SET content = content || E'\n\n## Practice Trade Setup: Bull Flag Breakout\n\n**Scenario:** AMD forms bull flag after strong impulse move\n\n**Setup Details:**\n- **Stock:** AMD (Advanced Micro Devices)\n- **Timeframe:** 1-Hour\n- **Pole:** $120 to $135 (+12.5% in 2 days)\n- **Flag:** 4-day consolidation between $132-$136\n\n**Pattern Measurements:**\n- Pole Height: $15 ($120 → $135)\n- Flag Duration: 4 days (8 candles on 4H)\n- Flag Retracement: 20% of pole (healthy < 38%)\n\n**Trade Execution:**\n1. **Entry:** $136.50 (break above flag resistance)\n2. **Stop Loss:** $131.50 (below flag low, $5 risk)\n3. **Target:** $151.50 (pole height added: $136.50 + $15)\n4. **Risk:Reward:** 1:3\n\n**Position Sizing:**\n- Account: $25,000\n- Risk: 2% = $500\n- Stop: $5\n- Position: $500 / $5 = 100 shares\n\n**Bull Flag Quality Check:**\n- [ ] Pole has angle > 45 degrees (strong impulse) ✓\n- [ ] Flag retraces < 50% of pole ✓\n- [ ] Flag duration: 3-15 bars ideal ✓\n- [ ] Volume decreasing during flag ✓\n- [ ] Breakout on above-average volume ✓\n\n**Flag vs Pennant:**\n- Flag: Parallel channel (rectangle)\n- Pennant: Converging trendlines (triangle)\n- Same measured move target applies to both'
WHERE slug = 'flags-pennants-trading';